creator: Stay Current: Pediatric Surgery
descriptionHtml:
Stay Current: Pediatric Surgery is a focused "one-stop-shop" for the Pediatric Surgery Professional. Stay Current is designed to provide easy access to the latest information about techniques in pediatric surgery and care. Stay Current contains the most current information from the best sources, such as the Journal of Pediatric Surgery, GlobalCastMD Videos & Podcasts, and worldwide journals. Stay Current has abstracts, full articles, videos, podcasts, links, guidelines and much more.

The Stay Current mobile app offers the most modern form of digital education for health care providers with a focus on pediatric surgery. It is built for the lifestyle of busy clinicians by allowing users to listen to audio chapters, read text chapters, or watch educational and surgical technique videos from a very robust library of 1000's of videos.

Users can comment on content, engage in discussions and join the growing community of Stay Current followers.

Now all pediatric surgery professionals can Stay Current with all of the most relevant journal publications, videos, podcasts and more.
descriptionShort: Stay Current is a focused "one-stop-shop" for the Pediatric Surgery Professional

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- More advanced, fast, and streamlined functionality & interface
- All sections of the app displayed in Carousels on the Home Screen for easy, quick, access
- The ability to bookmark favorite topics into a playlist for quick reference in the future
- Introducing “Storycasts” which allow users to test their knowledge.
- Fast forward or rewind videos with swiping
- Improved podcast functions: faster speed, saved where you left off, play when screen sleeps, easy to jump to sub-topics
- Much more!

==== New Private Channels ====
We've now added the ability for hospitals, associations and other organizations to have their own private apps inside the Stay Current app.

Hospital staff can now stay up-to-date on current information in Pediatric Surgery as well as take advantage of private discussions in the channel, staff directory, custom carousels (like playlists) and more - all without allowing these features to be available to the public.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: With this version, we have entirely redesigned the app, streamlining how you interact with the app and the content. First, we've moved the menu to the side bar, and replaced it with an actual "Home" Tab. Next, we've updated the search feature, providing an easier way to search for content, and filter down to what you're looking for. With Videos and Podcasts, we've updated how the chapters are displayed, making it easier to get to the specific topic you are looking for.

title: StayCurrent

creator: Stay Current: Pediatric Surgery
descriptionHtml:
StayCurrentMD is a focused "one-stop-shop" for the Medical Professional. StayCurrentMD is designed to provide easy access to the latest information about techniques in medical care. StayCurrentMD contains the most current information from the best sources, such as the Journal of Pediatric Surgery, GlobalCastMD Videos & Podcasts, and worldwide journals. StayCurrentMD has abstracts, full articles, videos, podcasts, links, guidelines and much more.

The StayCurrentMD mobile app offers the most modern form of digital education for health care providers. It is built for the lifestyle of busy clinicians by allowing users to listen to audio chapters, read text chapters, or watch educational and surgical technique videos from a very robust library of 1000's of videos.

Users can comment on content, engage in discussions and join the growing community of StayCurrentMD followers.
descriptionShort: StayCurrentMD is a focused "one-stop-shop" for the Medical Professional
